title: 10/20 Fantasy Football Podcast: Start or Sit (NFC), KC-OAK Recap
description:
Amari Cooper is back! Or is he??? We start with a recap of Thursday's awesome game (2:00) with Fantasy analysis on the OAK RBs and much more ... Introducing the No Touchdowns Club (21:00), plus "Beat the Waiver Wire (22:00)" for Week 8 ... JAC-IND (27:00), NO-GB (31:30), ARI-LAR (37:55), BAL-MIN (43:16), CAR-CHI (48:46), WAS-PHI (53:44), DAL-SF (1:00:15), SEA-NYG (1:01:55) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
 
To learn more about listener data and our privacy practices visit: https://www.audacyinc.com/privacy-policy
